songs.title: Jimmy Kane

Sex in pain
Keeps me alive, yeah

Mimicking no-one else
You can't fake it
You will never make it
You can't confuse yourself
Mimicking no-one else
You can't fake it
You will never make it

[Verse 2]
You're to blame
For everything

Keeps moving me
Keeps me

[Chorus]

You can't fake it
You will never make it
You can't confuse yourself
